# AI Model Licensing

ShortForge uses only open, commercially safe models.

## Components

- **Forge-Script**: Phi-3-mini (Microsoft, MIT) — quantized for CPU  
- **Forge-Scene**: SD-Turbo (Stability AI, RAIL-M) — fine-tuned on CC0 stock footage  
- **Forge-Voice**: Coqui TTS (MPL 2.0) — voices trained on public domain audiobooks  
- **Forge-Edit**: Custom OpenCV/FFmpeg pipeline (MIT)

## Rights

You may:
- Use generated videos for any purpose (personal/commercial)
- Modify and redistribute outputs
- Embed ShortForge in internal workflows

You may not:
- Redistribute model weights separately
- Claim ownership of base AI architectures

All processing is local. No data leaves your device.
